---

<Layout 
  title="ចុងភៅ ចេង គួងម៉េង - CKM Catering Service | សេវាកម្មម្ហូបការលំដាប់ខ្ពស់" 
  description="CKM Catering ផ្តល់ជូននូវសេវាកម្មម្ហូបការ ជប់លៀងក្រុមហ៊ុន និងចុងភៅផ្ទាល់ខ្លួនលំដាប់ខ្ពស់នៅភ្នំពេញ។ យើងផ្តោតលើគុណភាពអនាម័យ រសជាតិដើម និងសេវាកម្មស្តង់ដារអន្តរជាតិ។"
  image={heroImage}
>
  
  <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 top-0 left-0 bg-dark/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-white/10 shadow-lg transition-all">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-20">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <img src={logo} alt="CKM Logo" width="48" height="48" class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full border-2 border-gold shadow-glow">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg font-heading tracking-wider">ចុងភៅ ចេង គួងម៉េង</span>
            <span class="text-gold text-[0.6rem] tracking-wider uppercase font-chinese font-bold">CKM Catering Service</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <a href={telegramLink} target="_blank" aria-label="Contact us on Telegram" class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-2 text-white hover:text-primary transition">
              <i class="fab fa-telegram text-xl"></i>
              <span class="font-heading pt-1">តេឡេក្រាម</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#contact" aria-label="Go to Contact Section" class="bg-primary hover:bg-red-800 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm transition shadow-lg hover:scale-105 flex flex-col items-center leading-none justify-center border border-red-800/50">
              <span class="font-heading text-base mb-0.5">ទាក់ទងយើង</span>
              <span class="text-[0.6rem] font-chinese opacity-90">Contact Us | 联系我们</span>
            </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat bg-fixed transform scale-105" style={`background-image: url('${heroImage}');`}></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-black/50 to-dark"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-10">
        <img src={logo} alt="CKM Logo" width="128" height="128" class="w-32 h-32 md:w-44 md:h-44 rounded-full border-4 border-gold mx-auto mb-8 shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.5)]" fetchpriority="high">
        
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-heading leading-tight drop-shadow-2xl">
          ចុងភៅ <span class="text-gold">ចេង គួងម៉េង</span>
        </h1>

        <h2 class="text-lg md:text-2xl font-bold text-white/90 mb-6 font-chinese tracking-wide">
          Premier Catering Service | <span class="text-gold">金边顶级宴会餐饮</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-200 mb-8 font-light font-heading">
          សេវាកម្មម្ហូបការ និងកម្មវិធីជប់លៀងដ៏ល្អឥតខ្ចោះនៅភ្នំពេញ
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 justify-center animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
            <a href={telegramLink} target="_blank" aria-label="Chat on Telegram" class="bg-[#0077b5] hover:bg-[#005e93] text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,119,181,0.4)] flex items-center justify-center gap-3 group">
                <i class="fab fa-telegram-plane text-2xl group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition"></i> 
                <div class="flex flex-col items-start leading-none">
                    <span class="font-heading text-lg">ឆាតសួរព័ត៌មាន</span>
                    <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-chinese opacity-100">Telegram | 线上咨询</span>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+85512977696" aria-label="Call Now" class="bg-white hover:bg-gold text-dark hover:text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition flex items-center justify-center gap-3 shadow-lg group">
                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt text-primary group-hover:text-white text-xl"></i>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-start leading-none">
                    <span class="font-heading text-lg">ហៅទូរស័ព្ទ</span>
                    <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-chinese opacity-90 font-bold">Call Now | 立即致电</span>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <a href="#about" aria-label="Scroll Down" class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer group animate-bounce z-20">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/30 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-gold group-hover:border-gold transition duration-300 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)]">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-white text-sm group-hover:text-dark"></i>
        </div>
        <span class="text-[0.6rem] text-white/50 tracking-widest uppercase group-hover:text-white transition">Scroll</span>
    </a>
  </header>

  <section id="about" class="py-24 bg-dark relative overflow-hidden">
     <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-dark via-[#1a222e] to-dark pointer-events-none"></div>
     
     <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white font-heading mb-3">ហេតុអ្វីជ្រើសរើស <span class="text-gold">CKM?</span></h2>
            <h3 class="text-base text-gray-500 font-chinese mb-6 font-light tracking-wide">
              Why Choose Us? | 为什么选择我们?
            </h3>
            <div class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-primary mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
             <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 hover:border-gold/50 transition duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2 hover:bg-white/10 hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-gold/30 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition shadow-glow">
                    <i class="fas fa-gem text-3xl text-gold"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-heading">គុណភាពល្អឯក</h3>
                <h4 class="text-sm text-gold font-chinese mb-4 font-bold opacity-80">Top Quality | 顶级品质</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-200 mb-2 leading-relaxed">យើងខ្ញុំជ្រើសរើសតែគ្រឿងផ្សំស្រស់ៗ និងល្អបំផុត។</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-chinese">
                  Selected freshest ingredients. <br/> 
                  严选最新鲜、最优质的食材。
                </p>
             </div>
             
             <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 hover:border-gold/50 transition duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2 hover:bg-white/10 hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-gold/30 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition shadow-glow">
                    <i class="fas fa-star text-3xl text-gold"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-heading">បទពិសោធន៍</h3>
                <h4 class="text-sm text-gold font-chinese mb-4 font-bold opacity-80">Experience | 经验丰富</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-200 mb-2 leading-relaxed">បទពិសោធន៍ជាច្រើនឆ្នាំក្នុងការរៀបចំកម្មវិធី។</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-chinese">
                  Years of high-end event experience. <br/>
                  擁有多年承办高端宴会的经验。
                </p>
             </div>
             
             <div class="bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 hover:border-gold/50 transition duration-300 group hover:-translate-y-2 hover:bg-white/10 hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-gold/30 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition shadow-glow">
                    <i class="fas fa-concierge-bell text-3xl text-gold"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 font-heading">សេវាកម្ម</h3>
                <h4 class="text-sm text-gold font-chinese mb-4 font-bold opacity-80">Premium Service | 至尊服务</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-200 mb-2 leading-relaxed">ក្រុមការងារជំនាញរបស់យើងនឹងផ្តល់ជូននូវបទពិសោធន៍។</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-chinese">
                   Professional One-stop Service. <br/>
                   专业团队提供无微不至的服務。
                </p>
             </div>
        </div>
     </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-cream text-dark">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-2 font-heading text-dark">ដំណើរការសេវាកម្ម</h2>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-400 font-chinese mb-16 text-lg tracking-wide">
          Service Process | 服务流程
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
            <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-[16%] right-[16%] h-1 bg-gray-200 -z-10"></div>
            
            {serviceSteps.map(item => (
                <div class="text-center bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition relative group border-b-4 border-transparent hover:border-primary">
                    <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-primary text-white text-3xl rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-white shadow-md relative z-10 group-hover:bg-gold transition transform group-hover:rotate-12">
                        <i class={`fas ${item.icon}`}></i>
                        <span class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold border-2 border-white">{item.step}</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1 font-heading">{item.title}</h3>
                    <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-primary mb-3 font-chinese opacity-80">{item.subTitle}</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-base">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
            ))}
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="gallery" class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold text-dark font-heading mb-3">ស្នាដៃម្ហូបការរបស់យើង</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 font-chinese tracking-wide">
          Our Masterpieces | 宴会作品展示
        </p>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gold mx-auto mt-6 rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {gallery.map((img, index) => (
            <div class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 aspect-[4/3] cursor-pointer bg-gray-100">
                <img 
                    src={img} 
                    alt={`CKM Catering Gallery Wedding ${index + 1}`} 
                    width="800"
                    height="600"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700" 
                    loading="lazy" 
                    fetchpriority="low"
                />
            </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
       <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-dark font-heading mb-2">គន្លឹះ និងចំណេះដឹង</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 font-chinese tracking-wide">
            Insights & Guide | 专业宴会指南
          </p>
       </div>
       <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          {blogPosts.map(post => (
            <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 h-full flex flex-col">
               <a href={post.link} class="block aspect-[2/1] overflow-hidden relative">
                  <img src={post.image} alt={post.khTitle} width="800" height="400" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500"/>
                  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-transparent transition"></div>
               </a>
               <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark font-heading mb-2 group-hover:text-primary transition line-clamp-2">{post.khTitle}</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 font-chinese text-sm mb-4 line-clamp-2 font-bold opacity-80">{post.subTitle}</p>
                  <div class="mt-auto">
                      <a href={post.link} class="inline-flex items-center text-primary text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-red-700 transition">
                          Read More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2 text-xs"></i>
                      </a>
                  </div>
               </div>
            </div>
          ))}
       </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="py-24 bg-primary relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/stardust.png')] opacity-20"></div>
    <div class="absolute -left-20 -bottom-20 w-96 h-96 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-heading">ទាក់ទងមកយើងខ្ញុំ</h2>
      <h3 class="text-2xl text-white/90 font-chinese mb-8 tracking-wide">
        Contact Us Today | 立即联系我们
      </h3>
      <p class="text-xl text-red-100 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        កម្មវិធីដ៏ល្អឥតខ្ចោះមួយ ចាប់ផ្តើមពីការពិភាក្សាដ៏សាមញ្ញ។
        <br/>
        <span class="text-base font-chinese opacity-80 mt-2 block">
          A perfect event starts with a simple conversation. <br/>
          一场完美的活动，始于一次简单的沟通。
        </span>
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
        {phoneNumbers.map((contact) => (
            <a href={`tel:+855${contact.num.replace(/\s/g, '').substring(1)}`} aria-label={`Call ${contact.num}`} class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white hover:text-primary text-white border border-white/20 p-8 rounded-2xl transition duration-300 flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-lg">
                <i class={`fas ${contact.icon} text-4xl mb-2 text-gold group-hover:text-primary transition`}></i>
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold font-heading">{contact.num}</span>
                <span class="text-xs opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">{contact.type}</span>
            </a>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-8">
        <a href={facebookLink} target="_blank" aria-label="Facebook" class="w-16 h-16 bg-white text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl hover:scale-110 hover:bg-gold hover:text-white transition shadow-lg">
          <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
        </a>
        <a href={telegramLink} target="_blank" aria-label="Telegram" class="w-16 h-16 bg-white text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl hover:scale-110 hover:bg-gold hover:text-white transition shadow-lg">
          <i class="fab fa-telegram-plane"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
